          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1653317592218-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a baking tray with the <strong>spice mix</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and mix everything together until the chips are evenly coated in spices – these are your <strong>spiced fries</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
